# Backend (.NET 8)

## Patterns

- Controllers in `Simulyn.Api/Controllers/`, services in `Services/`, entities in `Models/Entities/`, DTOs in `Models/Dtos/`.
- Inject `OrganizationContext` for tenant scope; call `RequireRoleAsync(OrgRoles.Member|Admin|Owner)` before mutations.
- EF Core migrations in `Migrations/` — add via `dotnet ef migrations add` from `Simulyn.Api`.
- Config keys use `__` for nesting (e.g. `ConnectionStrings__Default`, `Stripe__ApiKey`).

## AI integration

- Call ai-service through `AiClientService`; respect `BudgetGuard` and rate limits on predictions/simulation/chat.
- Chat tool loop lives in `ChatOrchestrator.cs` + `ChatTools.cs` — tools are read-only, org-scoped.

## Tests

- Add xUnit tests in `Simulyn.Api.Tests` for billing, tenant isolation, and scenario math changes.
- Use `TestFactory` for integration-style controller tests.

## Errors

- Return ProblemDetails where the API already does; include trace id when available for support.
